### Modifications and Extensions

This repository builds upon the original **SEAL** project by Adam Zweiger et al.
(https://github.com/Continual-Intelligence/SEAL), distributed under the MIT License above.

All new content, experimental extensions, and documentation introduced in the
**STABLE: Gated Continual Learning for Large Language Models** project are
Â© 2025 William Hoy and Nurcin Celik and are also released under the same
MIT License for compatibility.

#### Major Modifications
- Implemented gated continual self editing for LoRA merges (EM, Bits, and KL thresholds)
- Added dynamic scaling and clipping procedures for edit acceptance control
- Extended continual editing pipeline and anchor sampling framework

